 Trump (1981); Stribling & Miller (1987)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"rxn_006\",\n      \"name\": \"Reductive amination of pyruvate \u2192 L-Alanine\",\n      \"inputs\": [\"mol_006\", \"mol_002\"],\n      \"outputs\": [\"mol_011\"],\n      \"environment\": \"Hydrothermal\",\n      \"agents\": [\"Pyrite\", \"Nickel sulfide\"],\n      \"conditions\": {\n        \"temperature\": \"25\u201370\u00b0C (298\u2013343K)\",\n        \"pressure\": \"high (5 bar)\",\n        \"catalyst\": \"Pyrite, Nickel sulfide\",\n        \"aqueous\": true,\n        \"other\": \"pH 7\u201311; Fe(II):Fe(III) 1:1\"\n      },\n      \"mechanism\": \"Pyruvate undergoes reductive amination with NH\u2083, Fe/Ni minerals, H\u2082 as reducing agent.\",\n      \"reasoning\": \"Hafenbradl et al. (1995); Barge et al. (2019); Kaur et al. (2024)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"rxn_007\",\n      \"name\": \"Cyanosulfidic chemistry: HCN/H\u2082S/UV/phosphate \u2192 \u03b1-aminopropionitrile\",\n      \"inputs\": [\"mol_003\", \"mol_015\"],\n      \"outputs\": [\"mol_007\"],\n      \"environment\": \"Surface\",\n      \"agents\": [\"Phosphate mineral\", \"Montmorillonite\"],\n      \"conditions\": {\n        \"temperature\": \"308K (35\u00b0C)\",\n        \"pressure\": \"1 atm\",\n        \"catalyst\": \"Phosphate minerals, Cu(I)/Cu(II) redox\",\n        \"aqueous\": true,\n        \"other\": \"UV irradiation\"\n      },\n      \"mechanism\": \"Photoredox cycling enables reductive homologation of HCN with H\u2082S to \u03b1-aminopropionitrile.\",\n      \"reasoning\": \"Patel et al. (2015); Ritson & Sutherland (2013)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"rxn_008\",\n      \"name\": \"HCN oligomerization \u2192 DAMN\",\n      \"inputs\": [\"mol_003\"],\n      \"outputs\": [\"mol_008\"],\n      \"environment\": \"Surface\",\n      \"agents\": [\"Montmorillonite\", \"TiO\u2082\"],\n      \"conditions\": {\n        \"temperature\": \"\u221223\u00b0C to 300K\",\n        \"pressure\": \"1 atm\",\n        \"ca